name: Bio Meki
description:
Inspired by a certain mouse character well loved by everyone around the world, BIO MEKI is designed by Kenneth Tang / Blackseed in Hong Kong. Produced in high quality resin and with moving silicone parts, this art collectible measures 5" x 3.5" x 2.5". We have limited sets available.

* Expected to ship January 2014.

name: Bio Dog
description:
Inspired by a certain dog character well loved by everyone around the world, BIO DOG is designed by Kenneth Tang / Blackseed in Hong Kong. Produced in high quality resin and with moving silicone parts, this art collectible measures 4.5" x 2.5" x 4.5". We have limited sets available.

* Expected to ship January 2014.

name: Night Walkers Art Print
description:
From the creative mind of Clogtwo comes this superb art print which is inspired by Toy Story characters. The latest art print from Clogtwo, this is limited to 25 pieces worldwide!

Limited Edition of 25
Signed and Numbered 
A2 - 16.5 X 23.4 Inches Archival Pigment Print 
300gsm Cotton Fine Art Paper

name: Bad Apple - imPURITY Edition
description:
Goin and Mighty Jaxx are proud to announce the final bad apple release and also MJ's last release for 2013. 

This Limited Edition figure is in full matt white and comes with a new accessory, the molotov cocktail, It is designed to fit perfectly with the Bad Apple. Also included is everyone's favourite hand grenade. This Collector's Edition will have a brand new box as well featuring new art by GOIN. Very rare sets will have a Gold molotov cocktail and grenade, inserted randomly. 

As a special giveaway to celebrate winning best resin at the Designer Toy Awards, collectors who buy a set will have one chance to win a custom chrome pink Bad Apple! A random few will also receive discount codes and even special gifts in your parcel!

This release is a Limited Edition of 50 sets worldwide!
* Expected to ship 1st Quarter 2014.

name: Brainlington OG
description:
*Due to crazy year end shipping traffic, the shipment was delayed for some time. Sorry for the wait and thank you for your patience!

We work together with prominent NYC graffiti artist EWOKONE to bring his trademark BRAINLINGTON design into a 3D form for the very first time! A unique design comprising of the words " EWOKONE NYC" on the brain matters itself, this intricate design took 1 year to complete. This is the original edition, based on the original colours of BRAINLINGTON,  limited to 200pcs worldwide. The design of the Brain says "EWOKONE NYC".

8" vinyl art figure
Blister packed in box
Limited Edition of 200

name: Hug the Killer - Black Edition
description:
Earlier this year, we were were browsing through Behance when Hug the Killer caught my eye. We thought the character look really amazing and it wil be great to produce it as an designer figure. We approached Nikopicto and they are as excited as us to make this happen. The story of Hug the Killer is as such, while his body language is very friendly and welcoming, even to the point of opening his arms to hug you, he has a set of razor sharp teeth that is opening into a grin. It makes you wonder if he indeed is genuinely happy to meet you or are you simply his dinner?

We feel that this actually mimics life, in terms of your relationship with the next person. Are they genuine? Or are they simply using you? Hug the Killer defines the moment when you have all these uncertainties and yet you find yourself slowly walking towards Hug, in truth, you will never know the answer.

Limited Edition of 100
4" tall high gloss art figure
Blister packed in box

description:
A recurring graphic in many of Clogtwo's works, this image is now produced into a 3D figure by Mighty Jaxx. This life sized SKUHL measures 20cm (width) X 16cm (height).

Casted in resin and finished in Matt Black, this beautiful piece is limited to 20 sets worldwide!

name: Giant Skuhl - White Edition
description:
A recurring graphic in many of Clogtwo's works, this image is now produced into a 3D figure by Mighty Jaxx. This life sized SKUHL measures 20cm (width) X 16cm (height).

Casted in resin and finished in Gloss white, this beautiful piece is limited to 50 sets worldwide!

name: Machine Mouth Art Book
description:
Machine Mouth: Engineered by Clogtwo is an extensive 368 pages hardcover art book that showcases Clogtwo's full body of work, from 2008 - 2012.

This book is a Limited Edition item and will not be restocked once it is sold out. This sales is for the art book itself.

name: Sailor Trixie
description:
*Due to crazy year end shipping traffic, the shipment was delayed for some time, it is now reaching our warehouse for fulfilment of orders. Sorry for the wait and thank you for your patience!

Popular UK 3D artist Andrew Hickinbottom and Mighty Jaxx proudly presents his latest figure, Sailor Trixie! Based on one of his  original character, Trixie is now fully decked in sexy Sailor wear! This is the first full body art figure that Andrew have created, we have spend an intensive 6 months to prep this figure. We have used the best techniques and materials to convey Andrew's creative ideas into a 3D figure. Sailor Trixie is double boxed in foam and with foam corners, to protect the fragile parts. This is truly an art collectible!

Sailor Trixie
6.5" tall with base
Limited Edition of 200
Foam packed, double boxed in cardboard box designed by Andrew.

name: Miss Mao - Silver Edition
description:
Miss Mao was initially created as a 2.5m tall sculpture, exhibiting in museums worldwide, a 50cm tall version was sold out at EUR15,000 each. To make art affordable to the everyday collector of art and toys, Mighty Jaxx and FLABSLAB worked with the world famous Gao Brothers to produce a space friendly 24cm tall resin version. Chromed silver and packaged in a laser etched wooden box, this highly acclaimed fine art piece is now available.

Limited Edition of 30
24cm (9.5") chrome silver fine art bust

name: Love Bomb - White Edition
description:
LOVE BOMB (aka FAT BOY) is an original life sized art sculpture by PHUNK, which was shown at their solo exhibition titled “Universality” at the Museum of Contemporary Art, Taipei in 2006. Based on the concept that "Love is the most powerful force in the world".  The atomic bomb is the ultimate symbol of mankind's creative genius and destructive nature. They created a technologically advanced object with a sole purpose and function of mass destruction. PHUNK wanted to build a LOVE BOMB to communicate and spread the message that the most powerful force in the world is actually Love.... only Love can change the world.... not bombs.

PHUNK worked with Mighty Jaxx to produce a smaller replica of the original Love Bomb. After a year in development, this 12" tall Love Bomb is now available! This is the white edition.

Limited Edition of 50
12″ resin figure

name: Hell Lotus Black Mamba
description:
Part of the Urban Oriental series, Hell Lotus reflects upon the play of local religious beliefs with a touch of urbanity – merging what Singapore is all about, an amalgation of deeply rooted religious beliefs, along with the modern fast paced society. Collaborating with one of the finest urban artist in Singapore, Clogtwo teamed up with Mighty Jaxx to produce our first art figure, the Hell Lotus.

Limited to only 50 sets worldwide.

8" vinyl art figure
Bagged with header card

name: Sideways
description:
Yoskay Yamamoto's latest art figure, SIDEWAYS, is based on his exhibited work of the same name at his solo show Joke's On Me. Staying true to his sculpture, Mighty Jaxx developed a production figure using a mixed media of wood and resin. It comes packaged in a blister cardboard box designed by Yoskay himself.

This is a special colourway of SIDEWAYS made exclusively for the Singapore Comic Con. 

Limited Edition of 100 worldwide
4" X 7" 4"
Wood (head) + Resin (body)
Blister in cardboard box
